  "id": "019ce975-c8c9-73a2-823a-4f7975f713f3",
  "content": "# Dashboard UX Overhaul — Architectural Decisions (2026-03-13)\n\n## Overview\nComplete overhaul of the corvia dashboard with 18 tasks across 5 chunks. All features implemented, tested, and pushed.\n\n## D1: K-Means Clustering with Shared Embedding Vocabulary\n- **Decision**: Single ClusterStore (k-means with k-means++ init) on 768-dim nomic-embed-text embeddings serves graph, activity feed, and agent summaries\n- **Why**: Avoids recomputing clusters per consumer; embeddings already exist on KnowledgeEntry\n- **Implementation**: `clustering.rs` — silhouette scoring (sampled, 10% or max 500) for optimal K (3..12), `ClusterHierarchy` with `SuperCluster` containing sub-cluster members\n- **Label resolution**: `build_with_labels()` accepts HashMap<String, String> mapping entry IDs to human-readable names (source_file or content preview). Without this, cluster labels are UUIDs.\n\n## D2: Multi-Tiered LOD Graph\n- **Decision**: 4-level LOD rendering: L0 super-clusters → L1 sub-clusters → L2 file groups → L3 individual entries\n- **Why**: Scales to thousands of entries without overwhelming the canvas\n- **Implementation**: Zoom-driven level switching with 0.05x hysteresis to prevent flickering. Viewport culling at L3 removes the old 500-edge hard limit. Breadcrumbs for navigation context.\n- **Endpoint**: GET /api/dashboard/graph/scope returns clustered node/edge data\n\n## D3: Activity Feed with Semantic Grouping\n- **Decision**: Activity feed replaces the old HistoryView UUID-lookup pattern\n- **Endpoint**: GET /api/dashboard/activity — reverse-chronological feed with semantic grouping\n- **Grouping rule**: Same agent + (same topic OR within 5-minute window) = grouped. Adjacent items only.\n- **Content deltas**: UTF-8 byte diff vs predecessor entry (positive = addition, negative = deletion)\n- **Topic tags**: Resolved from ClusterStore hierarchy via entry_labels map\n\n## D4: Collapsible Sidebar with Context-Aware Content\n- **Decision**: 3-state sidebar (collapsed/0px, narrow/320px, wide/480px) with SidebarContext\n- **Content types**: config, health, cluster, entry, agent, finding, history\n- **Auto-collapse**: Sidebar collapses on tab switch. Chevron toggle always visible at sidebar edge.\n- **Delay clear**: Content cleared 220ms after collapse to allow animation to finish\n\n## D5: Agent Identity System\n- **Decision**: `corvia agent connect` interactive CLI command + SessionStart hook reminder\n- **Implementation**: CLI prompts for agent selection from registered agents, establishes session\n- **Reconnectable agents**: GET /api/dashboard/agents/reconnectable returns agents with existing sessions\n- **Agent enrichment**: AgentRecord extended with `description` and `activity_summary` fields\n\n## D6: Cross-Tab Navigation\n- **Decision**: SidebarAPI includes `navigateToHistory(entryId)` for cross-tab deeplinks\n- **Implementation**: Any view can navigate to History tab with a specific entry pre-loaded (e.g., \"View history\" link in GraphView, agent cards, health findings)\n- **State**: `deeplinkEntryId` in Layout, cleared when leaving History tab\n\n## D7: Human-Readable Cluster Labels\n- **Decision**: All cluster label consumers must resolve UUID labels to human-readable names\n- **Pattern**: Build entry_labels HashMap<String, String> from entries (source_file or first 60 chars of content), pass to build_with_labels() or resolve at display time\n- **Callers updated**: activity.rs, mod.rs (graph endpoint, agent summary endpoint)",
